name: Pre-Race Session #1
description:
This workout aims to activate the fast-twitch muscles and prepare body and mind for race-pace efforts. Commonly referred to as -opening up the legs- to avoid feeling stale on race day. This session is generally performed the day before race-day, and after having an easy day or two.
